Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:43.58,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\frz2.121\frx2\fry349\pos(1496,508.4)}氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:43.58,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\frz2.121\frx2\fry349\pos(1489.6,393.2)}勇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:43.58,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\frz2.121\frx2\fry349\pos(550,440)}努
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:43.58,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\frz2.121\frx2\fry349\pos(552,512)}力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:38.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:43.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 大家寫一句自己喜歡的句子 下課時交上來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:53.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在糾結呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:56.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學已經想好要寫甚麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:59.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒 我也沒有頭緒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:04.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對了 我們來相互寫想讓對方做的事情怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:07.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,相互？想讓對方做的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:09.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:20.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想讓高木同學做的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:24.91,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\fs150\fad(950,0)\frz345.6\frx14\fry336\pos(510,826)}禁\N止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:24.91,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\fs150\fad(950,0)\frz355.1\frx4\fry352\pos(1391.2,691.2)}捉\N弄\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:24.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:28.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,把「不要再捉弄我了」這一信息…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:33.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 感覺這樣做衹會起反作用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:37.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定會被高木同學拿來取樂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:41.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要在不挑釁高木同學的前提讓她反省的句子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:46.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這可不簡單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:52.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 寫好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:54.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:55.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼交換看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.78,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\fs120\an7}維持現状
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:01.49,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\an4}忍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:01.49,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\an4}耐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:01.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:04.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「忍耐」?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:07.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:08.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,忍耐甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:11.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這是想讓我做的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:13.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:15.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,説來話長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她沒理解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:21.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是 説的太明白又會起反作用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:23.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:28.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你寫了甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:29.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「維持現狀」是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:34.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:38.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,希望西片能保持現在這樣容易捉弄的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:41.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學這傢伙 向我進攻了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:45.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原來如此 原來是這種較量嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:47.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我現在可算是搞明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:51.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咱們再來一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:53.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:57.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給我走着瞧 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:59.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今次輪到我進攻了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:03.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你寫好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:04.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}還沒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:15.86,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\frx0\fry12\move(1601.6,1210.8,1576.2,749)}柔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:15.86,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\frx12\fry10\move(1564.8,746.8,1558.4,270)}温
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:15.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就這樣 讓高木同學知道她不夠温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:18.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 等着受打擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:21.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:25.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學在煩惱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:30.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我覺得這都是因為高木同學不夠温柔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:34.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我剛剛才發現 西片的字寫得不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不如説 寫得很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:38.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你有在哪裏學過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒有啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:46.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我很喜歡西片寫的字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:00.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:02.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:07.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦 怎麼好像突然温柔起來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:09.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這究竟是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:13.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道説 衹是我沒有注意到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:16.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學其實很温柔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:21.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:26.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:36.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你臉上沾到東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:40.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 我想到好點子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:00.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼從西片開始揭曉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 不是同時嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:07.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你就別管了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:10.22,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\fs120\an4}不\N許\N再
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:10.22,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\fs120\an4}捉\N弄\N我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:15.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最後還是重寫了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:18.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的字果然寫得很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:19.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,甚麼 你的關注點是那裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:23.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,總之 不要再捉弄我了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:24.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:27.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你回答得太乾脆了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:31.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,儘量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:34.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 高木同學的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:35.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:39.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:44.84,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\fs120\pos(1402,632)}你\N臉\N上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:44.84,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\fs120\pos(800,918)}沾\N了\N墨\N汁\N哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:59.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是那時…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:03.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明剛才還在説儘量做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:05.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為 在説之前我就做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:22.21,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1300)\fs100\pos(256,524)}不\N要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:22.21,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1300)\fs100\pos(172,524)}大\N意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:22.21,Takagisan-text2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1300)\fs100\pos(1168,580)}不\N要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:22.21,Takagisan-text2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1300)\fs100\pos(1070,576)}大\N意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:28.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,換裝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:34.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:36.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:40.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是時候該換短袖了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:42.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:47.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也吿訴早苗明天開始穿短袖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:50.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:52.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你們在「是」甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:05.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你們倆不熱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:12.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:17.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是約好了要一起換裝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:19.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有這回事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:22.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有的 你搶跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:31.57,Takagisan-subtitle,,0,0,0,,{\fad(900,0)\fs150\blur2\pos(1412,504)}第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:37.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,短袖果然很涼快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:39.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:43.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你們在「是」甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:46.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:48.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上…好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:58.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是説要大家一起換嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:06.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我忘記説了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:13.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,疼疼疼疼疼…快放開我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:19.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,英譯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:21.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,That'right
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:24.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,Walk down this street to the post office
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,and turn left there
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,You will see the station
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,It takes five minute from here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:35.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天我一定要戰勝高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:38.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有甚麼好方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:44.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好久沒弄過嚇人盒子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:45.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是沒有材料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:48.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,現在開始做怕是來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:52.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 這一段…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:54.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:57.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:01.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,別「是」了 給我快點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,16
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:09.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是16
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:16.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這節不是數學課 是英語課 英語課
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:18.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我讓你翻譯這一段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:21.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,夠了 坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:27.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我都吿訴你是第16頁了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:31.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是故意讓我誤解的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:34.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒想到你真的誤解了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:36.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:39.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在想甚麼東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:42.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:44.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在想甚麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:50.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒甚麼 不是甚麼大事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:53.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:59.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是不是在想甚麼下流的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:01.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,甚麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:02.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:04.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:05.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:07.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,絕對沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:09.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:14.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其實是在想怎麼樣才能報復我平時的所作所為吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:18.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢…究竟是甚麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被我説中了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:24.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為你一直很在意我 我就在想是不是這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:27.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要明知故問嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:30.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為看西片的反應很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:34.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然後呢 想到甚麼好主意沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:39.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,當然 想到了絕佳的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:43.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定能奏效的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:47.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是真的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:50.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她一點也不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:53.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道她看穿了我甚麼也沒想出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:55.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然後呢 是甚麼主意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:58.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,説出來不就沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給我個提示也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:01.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:02.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比起這個 要好好聽課…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:06.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天是18號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:10.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學的學號也是18號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:12.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是能讓高木同學分心不聽課
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:16.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,讓她被點到時不知所措被老師臭罵一頓…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:18.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:21.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天早上你吃了甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:25.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,吃了山藥飯 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:28.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒甚麼 我就問問…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:32.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你喜歡山藥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:34.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 挺喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:37.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上吃了的話 感覺一整天都會很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:40.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 我也有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:42.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:44.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我嗎 我的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:46.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你猜猜看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:51.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想想 是米飯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,米飯算甚麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:55.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,甚麼 我以為你不喜歡吃麪包
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:57.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:59.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 雖然我喜歡吃米飯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:02.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很好 她的注意力轉移到課堂以外了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:05.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學也是米飯派嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:07.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我點人從頭開始讀下一頁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:10.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天是18號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:12.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:20.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 這下你不知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:24.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,I'll not do such a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:26.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 正確
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:27.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:33.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:36.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你 你在説甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:38.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡 還真有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:40.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不愧是高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:42.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,得想想下一招了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:45.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,果然還是要用嚇人盒子直接進攻…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:49.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 我不是沒材料嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:53.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 你在煩惱甚麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:57.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:14:00.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你又在想我的事情了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:06.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這種説法有點不太對…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:08.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且我才沒有想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:10.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:13.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那果然是下流的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都説不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:22.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我衹想着西片的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:24.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:27.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊哈 你臉紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:30.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:32.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:35.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,反正也是像現在這樣 想着要怎麼捉弄我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:45.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:50.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,剛剛那個停頓 搞甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:53.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼下一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:57.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為是6月18號 加起來是24號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:58.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:00.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:16.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,泳池開放的第一天竟然衹能在旁邊看着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:20.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是手沒有受傷的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:28.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真好啊 大家都很開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:34.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,泳池開放的第一天竟然衹能在旁邊看着 真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:36.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學也請假了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:37.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:42.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片是因為手上的傷口嗎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:49.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嘛 一言難盡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:52.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是想摸野貓然後被咬了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,甚麼 你為甚麼會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:56.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我明明沒吿訴過其他人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:16:01.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 猜對了嗎 我明明衹是隨口説的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:02.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你真笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:11.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學才是 為甚麼今天要請假…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話説起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:22.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,女生在游泳課的時候請假往往是因為生理期
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:26.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,課本上説 生理期時肚子會作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:29.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,保健體育課之王高尾是這麼説的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:32.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:37.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還是算了 感覺這是不能碰的高壓綫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:41.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,想問我為甚麼今天要請假嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:42.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被她聽見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:47.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,既然我猜中了西片受傷的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:49.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那今次輪到西片來猜了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:55.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,身體不適
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:57.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這種模稜兩可的答案可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:02.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算了吧 我也不想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:05.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那算我贏了可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:10.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我知道了 我猜就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:12.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,衹能猜一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:15.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然我覺得你肯定猜不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:17.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:21.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,信心滿滿地認為我説不出生理期這三個字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:23.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你可就太小看我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:26.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不對 她可是高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也有可能是在給我下套
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:34.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是我鼓起勇氣回答是生理期的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:36.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是呢 真沒禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,完全有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:43.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不對 她可是高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:47.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她肯定早就看穿我的想法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:49.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,連我會猶豫不決的事情也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:52.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然後再預料我的對策
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:58.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你連女生在游泳課時請假的原因都不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:00.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:03.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到底是陷阱還是真心話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:05.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還是偽裝成真心話的陷阱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:08.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還是裝作是陷阱其實是真心話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:11.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,越來越搞不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:15.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡啊 剛才她那表情究竟是甚麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:19.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其他的可能性呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:20.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比如受傷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好像沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:30.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看上去也不像是身體不適到無法運動的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:34.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 果然還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:35.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:43.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真好啊 大家都很開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:47.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我還要頂着酷暑絞盡腦汁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:50.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,和高木同學鬥智鬥勇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:53.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片你有好好在想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:57.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺你剛才開始一直看着在游泳的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:18:58.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才沒有看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:00.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:05.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都説男生衹知道盯着女生的胸部不放
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:07.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都説了我沒看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:12.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:14.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然這麼説有些對不起她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:15.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,胸有點平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:22.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,據説胸小的女生會格外在意胸部的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:25.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喜歡提前把午飯吃掉的木村這樣説過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:28.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道説 高木同學是因為對自己的胸部感到自卑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:31.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不去上游泳課的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:34.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你果然不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天也是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:39.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 我已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:43.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學在意自己胸部的大小吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:48.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這種話怎麼説得出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:50.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒禮貌也要有個限度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:54.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到頭來能回答的選項衹有生理期而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:56.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是那個也挺沒禮貌的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:20:00.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你還在想嗎 差不多到時間了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:04.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒事 課本上也有這些內容 不是甚麼令人羞恥的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒錯 堂堂正正地説出來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:14.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學請假的原因是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:17.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,生理期
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:23.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,猜錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:25.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在跟女孩子説甚麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:28.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 因為課本上也有寫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:29.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再説 一般而言…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:35.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 你臉紅到脖子根去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:41.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以答案是胸部的自卑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:44.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:50.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,順帶一提
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:21:05.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為胸部太小感到難為情也是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:07.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:10.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我還是想去游泳 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:12.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:16.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那她為甚麼要請假…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:20.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 也欣賞到了西片有趣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:21.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,去游一會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:26.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道説 你是為了捉弄我才請假的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:34.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等手的傷好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:39.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我們一起去游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:50.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:56.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,別被她騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:22:01.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要真和她去游泳了 她又會想着要捉弄我了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.46,0:22:04.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學就是這樣的人
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
