Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.37,0:00:29.75,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在校園的庭院 第一個發現你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:38.01,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}今天要和你說些什麼呢 即便是想著這些也是一種樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.05,0:00:40.97,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}窗簾隨風起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:46.35,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不經意地投入一束陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:50.28,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那美麗的容顏笑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:54.15,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}羞得我抬不起頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:01:02.25,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風兒喧囂 似要吹散考試的憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:10.55,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}吶 我想要和你一起 立下兩人的秘密約定
