Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.11,0:22:25.44,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}狂風中不知飛向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.44,0:22:29.95,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}怎麼會這樣 對我這麼冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.95,0:22:32.95,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}洋洋自得的酒窩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.95,0:22:36.96,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}稍微 有點心動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.96,0:22:47.88,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}其實 你是重視我而認真批評我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:56.60,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}如果這樣說的話你一定會洋洋得意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.06,0:22:59.81,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}所以再也不會表揚你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:05.28,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}單調乏味的命運 我早已厭倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.53,0:23:12.12,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}用未知的言語 解放我 好嗎
